\c 12
\s Abasizi bakaDavida eZikilagi
\p
\v 1 Laba-ke yilabo abeza kuDavida eZikilagi, lapho esavalelwe ngenxa kaSawuli indodana kaKishi; njalo babephakathi kwamaqhawe, abasizi bempi\x + 1 Sam. 27.1-6. Josh. 15.31.\x*.
\v 2 Behlomile ngamadandili\x + 2 Lan. 17.17. Hlab. 78.9.\x*, besebenzisa isandla sokunene lesokhohlo ngamatshe, langemitshoko ngedandili; babengababafowabo bakaSawuli koBhenjamini\x + Hlu. 3.15. 20.16.\x*.
\v 3 Inhloko yayinguAhiyezeri, loJowashi, amadodana kaShemaha umGibeya\x + Josh. 18.28.\x*; loJeziyeli loPeleti amadodana kaAzimavethi, loBeraka, loJehu umAnathothi\x + 11.28. 27.12. Josh. 21.18.\x*,
\v 4 loIshmaya umGibeyoni\x + Josh. 9.3.\x*, iqhawe phakathi kwabangamatshumi amathathu njalo ephezu kwabangamatshumi amathathu; loJeremiya, loJahaziyeli, loJohanani, loJozabadi umGedera\x + Josh. 15.36.\x*,
\v 5 uEluzayi, loJerimothi, loBeyaliya, loShemariya, loShefathiya umHarufi,
\v 6 uElkana, loIshiya, loAzareli, loJowezeri, loJashobeyamu, amaKora\x + 6.22,66,68,69. 12.26. 9.19.\x*,
\v 7 loJowela, loZebhadiya, amadodana kaJehoramu weGedori\x + Josh. 15.58.\x*.
\v 8 LakwabakoGadi bazehlukanisela kuDavida enqabeni enkangala, amaqhawe alamandla, amadoda ebutho empi, ephatha isihlangu esikhulu lomkhonto, obuso bawo babuyibuso bezilwane\x + 12.24. Nani 25.7. 2 Lan. 25.5.\x*, enjengemiziki ezintabeni ngesiqubu\x + 2 Sam. 2.18.\x*.
\v 9 UEzeri wayeyinhloko, uObhadiya owesibili, uEliyabi owesithathu,
\v 10 uMishimana owesine, uJeremiya owesihlanu,
\v 11 uAthayi owesithupha, uEliyeli owesikhombisa,
\v 12 uJohanani owesificaminwembili, uElizabadi owesificamunwemunye,
\v 13 uJeremiya owetshumi, uMakibanayi owetshumi lanye.
\v 14 Laba babengabamadodana akoGadi, izinhloko zebutho; omunye wabancinyane wayephethe ikhulu, lomkhulu wayephethe inkulungwane.
\v 15 Laba yibo abachapha iJordani ngenyanga yokuqala lapho yayigcwele iphuphuma inkumbi zonke zayo, baxotsha bonke \add ababese\add*zigodini ngempumalanga langentshonalanga\x + Eks. 12.2. Josh. 3.15.\x*.
\v 16 Basebefika bevela ebantwaneni bakoBhenjamini labakoJuda enqabeni kuDavida.
\v 17 UDavida wasephuma ukubahlangabeza, waphendula wathi kibo: Uba lisiza kimi ngokuthula ukungisiza, ngilenhliziyo ehlangene lani\x + Hlu. 18.14.\x*; kodwa uba kuyikunginikela ngenkohliso ezitheni zami, kungelabubi ezandleni zami, uNkulunkulu wabobaba kakubone, ajezise\x + Gen. 20.16. 21.25. 24.44. 31.42.\x*.
\v 18 UMoya wasesehlela kuAmasayi inhloko yezinduna\x + 2 Sam. 17.25.\x*, \add wasesithi\add*: \add Si\add*ngabakho, Davida, \add si\add*lawe, ndodana kaJese! Ukuthula, ukuthula kube kuwe, lokuthula kube kubasizi bakho, ngoba uNkulunkulu wakho uyakusiza\x + 1 Sam. 25.6.\x*! UDavida wasebemukela, wabenza induna zeviyo.
\v 19 Abavela koManase bahlamukela kuDavida ekufikeni kwakhe lamaFilisti emelene loSawuli empini. Kodwa kababasizanga, ngoba ababusi bamaFilisti bamxotsha ngecebo besithi: Ngamakhanda ethu uzahlamukela enkosini yakhe uSawuli\x + 1 Sam. 29.2-9.\x*.
\v 20 Ekuyeni kwakhe eZikilagi kwabalekela kuye abavela koManase: OAdina loJozabadi loJediyayeli loMikhayeli loJozabadi loElihu loZilethayi, inhloko zezinkulungwane ababengabakoManase.
\v 21 Bona basebesiza kanye loDavida bemelene leviyo elihlaselayo, ngoba bonke babengamaqhawe alamandla, bezinduna ebuthweni\x + 1 Sam. 30.8. 1 Sam. 30.1-10.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba ngesikhathi insuku ngensuku beza kuDavida ukumnceda baze babe libutho elikhulu njengebutho likaNkulunkulu\x + 1 Sam. 14.15. Gen. 23.6. Jobe 1.16.\x*.
\s Ibutho likaDavida eHebroni
\p
\v 23 Lala ngamanani ezinhloko ezazihlomele impi\x + 2 Lan. 20.21. 28.14.\x*; zeza kuDavida eHebroni\x + 11.1. 2 Sam. 2.3,4. 5.1.\x* ukuphendulela umbuso kaSawuli kuye\x + 10.14.\x*, ngokomlomo weN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 11.3,10.\x*.
\v 24 Abantwana bakoJuda bethwele isihlangu esikhulu lomkhonto babeyizinkulungwane eziyisithupha lamakhulu ayisificaminwembili, behlomele impi\x + 12.24. Nani 25.7. 2 Lan. 25.5.\x*.
\v 25 Ebantwaneni bakoSimeyoni, amaqhawe alamandla empi, izinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa lekhulu.
\v 26 Ebantwaneni bakoLevi, izinkulungwane ezine lamakhulu ayisithupha\x + 12.6.\x*.
\v 27 LoJehoyada wayeyisiphathamandla sabakoAroni; kanye laye kwakulezinkulungwane ezintathu lamakhulu ayisikhombisa.
\v 28 LoZadoki ijaha, iqhawe elilamandla; lendlini kayise izinduna ezingamatshumi amabili\x + 6.8.\x*.
\v 29 Lebantwaneni bakoBhenjamini, abafowabo bakaSawuli, izinkulungwane ezintathu; ngoba kuze kube khathesi ubunengi babo bagcina uthembeko endlini kaSawuli\x + 2 Sam. 2.8,9. 3.19.\x*.
\v 30 Lebantwaneni bakoEfrayimi, izinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lamakhulu ayisificaminwembili, amaqhawe alamandla, amadoda alamabizo endlini yaboyise\x + 2 Sam. 2.8,9. 3.19.\x*.
\v 31 Lengxenyeni eyodwa kwezimbili yesizwe sakoManase, izinkulungwane ezilitshumi leyisificaminwembili, ababeqanjwe ngamabizo ukuthi beze babeke uDavida abe yinkosi\x + Nani 1.17.\x*.
\v 32 Lebantwaneni bakoIsakari, ababelokwazi beqedisisa izikhathi ukwazi ukuthi uIsrayeli ufanele enzeni, izinhloko zabo zazingamakhulu amabili, labafowabo bonke babesemlayweni wazo\x + Esta 1.13.\x*.
\v 33 KoZebuluni, abaphuma impi, behlela impi ngazo zonke izikhali zempi, izinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amahlanu, ukugcina iviyo kungengenhliziyombili\x + 12.36.\x*.
\v 34 LakoNafithali, izinduna eziyinkulungwane, labayizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu lesikhombisa kanye lazo, belesihlangu esikhulu lomkhonto.
\v 35 LakwabakoDani, abahlela impi, izinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lesificaminwembili lamakhulu ayisithupha.
\v 36 LakoAsheri\x + 2 Sam. 2.8,9. 3.19.\x*, abaphuma ebuthweni, ukuhlela impi, izinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane\x + 12.36.\x*.
\v 37 Lababevela ngaphetsheya kweJordani, kwabakoRubeni labakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase, belezikhali zonke zempi ukuyakulwa, izinkulungwane ezilikhulu lamatshumi amabili\x + 2 Sam. 2.8,9. 3.19.\x*.
\v 38 Wonke lamadoda empi, angagcina iviyo, afika eHebroni ngenhliziyo epheleleyo ukubeka uDavida abe yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli wonke; njalo loIsrayeli wonke oseleyo wayenhliziyonye ukubeka uDavida abe yinkosi\x + 1 Kho. 8.61.\x*.
\v 39 Njalo baba lapho loDavida insuku ezintathu besidla benatha, ngoba abafowabo babebalungisele.
\v 40 Futhi lababeseduze labo kuze kube koIsakari lakoZebuluni lakoNafithali baletha isinkwa ngabobabhemi langamakamela langezimbongolo langezinkabi\x + 1 Sam. 27.9.\x*, ukudla, impuphu, izinkwa zomkhiwa\x + 1 Sam. 30.12.\x*, lamahlukuzo ezithelo zevini ezonyisiweyo, lewayini, lamafutha, lezinkabi, lezimvu, ngobunengi, ngoba kwakulentokozo koIsrayeli\x + 1 Sam. 25.18.\x*.